        <h4>Registering a New Piece of Equipment</h4>
        <p>Click on "Register Equipment" from the home page. Fill in the name, type, cost, room, and your name. The date is added automatically.</p>

        <h4>Searching for Equipment</h4>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>By Room:</strong> Select a room to see all equipment stored there.</li>
            <li><strong>By Name:</strong> Enter the full name of the equipment.</li>
            <li><strong>By Type:</strong> Select a type from the list (e.g., Desktop PC, Monitor).</li>
        </ul>

        <h4>Editing or Deleting Equipment</h4>
        <p>After searching, click on a specific equipment entry to view its details. From there, you can choose to update or delete it.</p>

        <h4>Need More Help?</h4>
        <p>If something isn't working as expected, ensure all form inputs are valid.</p>
